-- Intesa Sanpaolo launches 7-year senior bond worth 1 billion euro-source
-- By Alessia Pe
-- Tue Jun 10, 2014 06:28AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 10 (Reuters) - Intesa Sanpaolo <ISP.MI> has launched a seven-year senior bond worth 1 billion euros ($1.36 billion), a source close to the deal said on Tuesday.

